  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to House",
    "asOf": "2022-10-07",
    "date": "2022-10-14T00:38:11Z",
    "text": "Abandoned Well Remediation Research and Development Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a research, development, and demonstration program with respect to (1) data collection on the location of abandoned oil or gas wells; (2) the plugging, remediation, reclamation, and repurposing of the wells; and (3) mitigating potential environmental impacts of documented and undocumented abandoned wells."
